{"tid":1626250,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[正視廳]今晚係和理非文宣之夜","createTime":"2019-10-05T10:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T10:50:44.000Z","uid":138264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e4d903ef517be1dd8f0a3a9dc4c47157263f7d15","tid":1626250,"uid":138264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:22:12.000Z","msg":"18區遍地文宣<br />\n放映會人鏈摺紙鶴<br />\n連儂文宣解釋返我地琴晚點解要咁做<br />\n同埋聽日大遊行 都冇乜人知<br />\n<br />\n仲有啲咩應該裝修 咩唔裝修<br />\n一芳 上海商業銀行 法院 vans 依啲共識黎 唔搞<br />\n圖書館 中資書店啲書 唔用火水魔法<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地只裝修 不搶劫 我地唔係賊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過 如果手足決定今晚勇武都唔會割 但係我地已經冇乜目標 只可以等佢修復再裝修過 請諗下今晚仲可以做啲咩先再行動</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你要聽日聚到300萬人 今晚一定要大大力宣傳<br />\n<br />\n聽日我要聽到一般市民話依個政府冇諗過妥協 仲強推條惡法係痴線"},{"pid":"24be70c92fbdd0518cc15b87e1e314285501060f","tid":1626250,"uid":138264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:22:40.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"3cc145bd63a9e786dda94869120a0ad5bb96bb9c","tid":1626250,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:24:55.000Z","msg":"毋忘721 831<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LNA1rbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLNA1rbb.jpg&h=295c7b1d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Fbge4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Fbge4w.jpg&h=a5ac864e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XThGrbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXThGrbc.jpg&h=87bf71d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e5a1a2f33142c525df39bdae25878c1655c25ef","tid":1626250,"uid":138264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:26:17.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"4bbc92f9920cee12d4c2065e7b8e002859e60b28","tid":1626250,"uid":138264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-